metadata.name: True Calling
metadata.description:
This collection is a manifestation of love, health, abundance, and courage for all of us as we embark in 2022.

May we embody our true calling  
May we align with our creativity  
May we move with purpose 
May we serve as a channel to heal the world 
May we build meaningful relationships 
May we find our Center, our Peace
